;          http://www.dfanning.com/programs/pickcolor.pro
;
; PROCEDURE:
;
;       Clicking the left mouse button allows you to drag a rubberband box
;       over the portion of the window you want to zoom into.
;
; EXAMPLE:
;
;        IDL> ZOOMBOX
;
